Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:26.49,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:28.76,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}渾身上下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:34.16,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}都在奮力呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:36.60,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}因僅憑一顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:38.75,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}拚盡全力生息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:42.60,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}苦痛纏身在即
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.74,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要踏出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.84,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}世界就會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.28,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}想像外的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.54,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}也能現於眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:54.87,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只需相信便好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:02:01.78,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}鐵杵尚能磨成針
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:03.82,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}你我一定也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:06.98,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要我們在一起
